{"tid":2394748,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 ！！香港警察更加應該知法犯法？（知法守法先啱）","createTime":"2021-02-04T11:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T02:49:24.000Z","uid":30886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa8d951022d78b77d01c8ffaf625e2fa0836e79","tid":2394748,"uid":30886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"早前警務處處長一哥話，香港警察更加應該知法犯法。（知法守法先啱）<br />\n<br />\n咁身為執法者犯法係咪應該要嚴懲，有見及此本人在此集思廣益，理性討論，執法者犯法應否設立一個最少嘅刑罰為起點嘅罰則，以保障市民，維護社會繁榮穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以阻嚇作用唔好俾呢啲害群之馬出現<br />\n<br />\n例如：執法者犯任何法律，小至亂拋垃圾，大至性侵、強姦、非禮等等，總之係犯法都應該最少監禁10年為起點，再加現有判刑監禁（即一般市民強姦犯法要監禁5年，咁執法者就要10+5，監禁15年）<br />\n亂拋垃圾被定罪就要監禁10年咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且不能以認罪及求情減刑。<br />\n<br />\n出發點唔係針對任何人，就好似港區國安法，都只係針對少數有機會會危害國家安全嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然執法者應該知法守法咁佢哋唔犯法咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4121417643f9fab8f297e3b9770e1bcb692d1c9c","tid":2394748,"uid":30886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T17:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d6f2c2b1b2200404ee3eb8bc0d3f29bcb5d4e1","tid":2394748,"uid":30886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7879d22e88009fbe4b311bca7dd007101e7841","tid":2394748,"uid":291487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:39:50.000Z","msg":"唔知咪唔洗守咁解"},{"pid":"306a368c15e83be6c352cc2bfd785e395bf5378a","tid":2394748,"uid":30886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c7879d22e88009fbe4b311bca7dd007101e7841","tid":2394748,"uid":291487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-0